metadata.name: Metaverse Nights Issue #01
metadata.description: Metaverse Nights Issue #1 by MultiNFT.io is an AI-designed, educational comic book that takes readers on a journey through the world of web3 and the Metaverse. Based on the MultiNFT Genesis Collection characters, it offers an immersive experience that highlights the potential and use of virtual worlds, digital collectibles, and fan engagement
